    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1891-11-04T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1891-11-04T00:00:00-05:00" n="34" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d34">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Conger</persName> to Mr.
                                <persName type="to">Blaine</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of
                                    the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Rio de
                                    Janeiro</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1891-11-04">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 4,
                            1891</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. Conger reports that, owing to fear of plots for the restoration of the
                        monarchy, the President had on this date by decrees dissolved Congress and
                        declared martial law.</p>
            </div>
